Dear {{agent_name}},

I came across your listing for {{property_address}} and I'm very interested in learning more about this property. Could you please provide additional information about its current condition, including any recent renovations or issues I should be aware of?

Also, I would appreciate if you could share more pictures of both the interior and exterior of the home.

Thank you for your assistance. I look forward to your response.

{{your_name}}
{{your_phone}}
{{your_email}}
